3.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathgeneral.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=15416.topic&index=79>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: no we're not and any of you who say we are are fools!</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> <br>
So, when uber_mob_00 kills your MA, what classes can jump in, get aggro and survive long enough to get the CH chain going? The rogue can. The monk can. The beastlord can. The ranger can. The bard can. Another warrior can. Nope, I don't see the 'defensive' hybrid in there anywhere. <br>
